snippet.title: Patrick Solomon
snippet.description:
Massive amounts of Gratitude to YOU for checking out my channel!

Hi I'm  Patrick Solomon, filmmaker and the creator of Finding Joe.  I'm officially dedicating the rest of my life to creating inspirational content.

Currently working on "WHAT IS MONEY"... a film about Money.
